author: plexiglass
title: Airline memories
review:
I remember getting these when I flew on Lufthansa many years ago. Not particulary impressed since it took a couple of minutes to put together- and flights are several hours long, which seem endless for a child.

Playing with a toy plane on a plane seems counterintuitive. Still, it brings back memories of my childhood. And its pieces are pretty good. I think I have 2 of these sets.
